genevese.d:
a. Of or pertaining to Geneva, in Switzerland; Genevan.
n. sing. & pl. A native or inhabitant of Geneva;
   collectively, the inhabitants of Geneva; people of Geneva.

germanize.d:
v. t. To make German, or like what is distinctively German;
   as, to Germanize a province, a language, a society.
v. i. To reason or write after the manner of the Germans.
